            "descriptionRaw": "Gathering a great number of gems, Ningguang scatters them all at once, sending homing projectiles at her opponents that deal massive <color=#FFE699FF>Geo DMG</color>.\nIf Starshatter is cast when a Jade Screen is nearby, the Jade Screen will fire additional gem projectiles at the same time.\n\n<i>Stars shatter. Silence falls.</i>",
            "name": "Starshatter"
        },
